Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八幕\N布洛涅之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然进来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.24,0:02:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我怎么叫你都不回答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香榭丽舍的客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说今日不想见您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么口信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没什么特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望能赏光参观新别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请您参加晚会的请贴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必与家人同往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣幸之至
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:02:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奥特伊的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:04:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Banner;12;0;90,{\a6}{\fs20}Auteuil：巴黎西部市郊的一个区，莫里哀等作家喜爱居住的地方。周围是布洛涅（Boulogne）森林。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么荒凉的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这是伯爵的个人意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…似乎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是属于维尔福先生的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的女主人在时 这里非常华丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是瓦朗蒂娜的亲生母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时还是年轻貌美的女士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是维尔福夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是外子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首席检察官大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说内人与犬子承蒙关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得您赏光亲临 实在蓬荜生辉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座别墅用来招待客人还稍显冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 不知为何我特别喜欢清静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 如今代表巴黎的三位绅士都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金融王唐格拉尔氏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌揽军队实权的莫尔塞夫将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有司掌法律的您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日招待各位参加这个简陋的聚会不为别桩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我向大家坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅者是不安之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望能和三位建立友情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军阁下是否渴望大统领的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您从何处听闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请让我略尽绵薄之力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 你先离席一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人之间有话要谈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 呆坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸色不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没事 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬拉你过来 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵…是不是在避开我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在维尔福先生家看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…伯爵和夫人有染
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候伯爵发现了我在偷窥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像…是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵也有不为人知的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是一个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你不是为了马克西米利安的事而去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是另外一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能与二位相伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去吹吹夜风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在…在下是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安·莫雷尔大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是位杰出的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下猎犬座γ方面军陆军上尉 马克西米利安·莫雷尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本家在马赛从事贸易 在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 在下和令媛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您从事着保卫国家的高尚工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我对表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但您只是一介平民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而小女已有未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 望您谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是越洋而来的马赛风味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求婚怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…她对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么悄悄话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博尚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然突然对首席检察官按下快门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够胆大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到嚣张的家伙就叛逆心理作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 青春的烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 这世上一个二个都为情所困
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 以前那两人也传过绯闻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首席检察官和欧仁妮的母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不情之请 实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 请别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钢琴课也花了不少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得在这种时候露两手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听我说两句
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想向您道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我…未考虑您的想法就出言不逊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦事都丢给你了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧仁妮那家伙弹得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被她骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会儿跟她聊过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是我说坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还来找我干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看见怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我在这里…把那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐就如您的天职
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天职吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵认识很多有才能的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您出色的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为展示年轻人们的才华横溢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容我再引荐一位年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈亚·卡瓦尔坎蒂侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家族还有继承人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的父亲是我的旧友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若大家能像待我一样待他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便不胜荣幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是刚继承亡父领地的后生晚辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他的胸饰 看样子值500万
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵的新宠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能非常有才华哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 抱歉打断各位畅谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能承蒙稍微侧目一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买下这座别墅是为了远离城市喧嚣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过清静离群的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但说来也奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际来到这里的我迷上了这幢古宅的某种气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:13:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该如何形容呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不禁去想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前这座别墅里人们过着怎样的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是隐藏了怎样不为人知的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次想起 我都充满着无以言表的喜悦和平稳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊 说什么诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检察官大人察觉不到这座宅子里阴郁邪恶的气氛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首席检察官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么由您亲自来确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实在这座宅子里只留有一间未使用的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那房间被认为是这邪恶气氛弥漫的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒谬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了 不要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就遵从一下主人的意愿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来参观一下这间邪恶的房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去的话 也无甚兴味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有欧仁妮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成三组去寻找那间房 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让三个年轻人先行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗宅邸至深之处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将赠予平安到达的人一份薄礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝先生 拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了 侯爵夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您气色不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请认真一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先发方能制人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一问 侯爵出身何处？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我来自银河东方的远方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一片非常美丽的行星群
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中某颗星上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一种吸取矿石菁华 孕育宝石之卵的鸟类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50年1次为繁殖而筑巢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能和您单独交谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 我想和您谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 莫尔塞夫夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶气氛的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您为何对马赛如此介怀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此话怎讲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的菜肴也安排了马赛口味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是看到您就想起以前认识的某人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来 我都只为再见他一面而活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在不知为何却感到恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不是孤独一人 绝不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人一直想念着您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要忘了那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是亡父给我的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您能收下它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到尽头了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧 阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔福先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否感到愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这座别墅奇异的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这宅邸的主人看来不知何为待客之道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请帮我一个小忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您如此帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了 在维尔福先生家的温室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 您看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人太热情了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为您一定非常生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 应该由我说对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也无法与您畅谈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我在远方宇宙得了一种病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时会不见任何人来修养
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔会感到麻痹而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 这是只属于你和我的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我会保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 拿着这个盒子出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…那孩子出生的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…是那孩子把我们引来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是17年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是伯爵送的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准恋人们的毒针
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那毒手也会降临到自己头上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话 岩窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九幕\N梦见黑暗之梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然后期待
